7
00:02:30,774 --> 00:02:31,774
Come on!

8
00:02:43,739 --> 00:02:45,163
Oh no, not the cellar.

9
00:02:48,187 --> 00:02:49,752
Run to the thresher, babe.

10
00:03:13,351 --> 00:03:14,394
Run!

11
00:03:14,498 --> 00:03:15,498
Run!

12
00:03:23,605 --> 00:03:25,134
Mom, come on!

13
00:03:53,356 --> 00:03:54,886
I love you!

14
00:04:00,726 --> 00:04:01,726
Mom!

15
00:04:04,444 --> 00:04:05,444
Mom!

16
