The boy and his mother are
running from a tornado,

17
00:04:18,556 --> 00:04:20,711
and they come to a wheat thresher.

18
00:04:20,815 --> 00:04:23,108
Then the mother gets sucked up into the air.

19
00:04:23,213 --> 00:04:25,681
And the boy grabs on,
but he's not strong enough,

20
00:04:25,785 --> 00:04:27,001
and he lets her go.

21
00:04:27,105 --> 00:04:29,226
She flies up into the air.

22
00:04:29,330 --> 00:04:31,868
