Stacy.

24
00:04:56,441 --> 00:05:00,055
I don't think it's going
to be a permanent thing.

25
00:05:00,159 --> 00:05:01,159
Stacy?

26
00:05:05,095 --> 00:05:06,095
Stacy.

27
00:05:09,474 --> 00:05:10,474
Oh.

28
00:05:15,731 --> 00:05:17,608
I'm not in the mood to
explain why Jake still

29
