I had a great time last night.

31
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:28,591
Me too.

32
00:05:28,695 --> 00:05:30,502
So, are you going to call me?

33
00:05:30,607 --> 00:05:31,607
Of course.

34
00:05:31,685 --> 00:05:34,708
You didn't call Louisa.

35
00:05:34,813 --> 00:05:36,028
Louisa?

36
00:05:36,133 --> 00:05:36,884
Well...

37
00:05:36,899 --> 00:05:38,740
It's OK move on you know.

38
00:05:38,844 --> 00:05:40,477
Yeah.

39
00:05:40,582 --> 00:05:42,180
That's what I was doing last night.

40
00:06:09,395 --> 00:06:11,550
It was a story, mom, just a story.

41
00:06:11,655 --> 00:06:13,183
I don't see what the big deal is.

42
00:06:13,288 --> 00:06:15,409
The big deal is that you're
the only one who seems

43
