to think it has a happy ending.

44
00:06:17,842 --> 00:06:19,545
It wasn't a happy ending.

45
00:06:19,650 --> 00:06:22,395
It was just scary.

46
00:06:22,499 --> 00:06:23,499
It was fun to tell.

47
00:06:26,601 --> 00:06:30,389
Campbell, honey,
I know that you are angry about the move

48
00:06:30,493 --> 00:06:31,242
here.

49
00:06:31,257 --> 00:06:32,787
I'm not angry.

50
00:06:32,891 --> 00:06:34,630
It's not my story.

51
00:06:34,734 --> 00:06:36,054
Jake told it to me.

52
00:06:36,158 --> 00:06:37,584
Jake?

53
00:06:37,688 --> 00:06:39,251
Did Jake?

54
00:06:39,357 --> 00:06:40,398
Jake told you that story?

55
00:06:40,504 --> 00:06:41,511
Uh-huh.

56
00:06:46,308 --> 00:06:49,853
Hey,
did you see that girl he had over last night?

57
00:06:49,957 --> 00:06:51,173
She was so hot.

58
