1124
01:14:05,868 --> 01:14:07,049
All right.

1125
01:14:07,153 --> 01:14:09,240
Deputy, got any word on that diesel fuel?

1126
01:14:09,344 --> 01:14:12,437
It's Jake.

1127
01:14:12,541 --> 01:14:13,758
Jake, is Campbell all right?

1128
01:14:17,720 --> 01:14:19,597
Mom?

1129
01:14:19,702 --> 01:14:21,857
Oh, baby, hi.

1130
01:14:21,961 --> 01:14:23,524
Are you all right? Are you hurt?

1131
01:14:23,629 --> 01:14:24,622
Mom, I'm OK.

1132
01:14:24,637 --> 01:14:27,070
Jake found me.

1133
01:14:27,174 --> 01:14:29,607
You are a very, very brave boy.

1134
01:14:29,711 --> 01:14:30,711
