Pull over.

1183
01:18:11,287 --> 01:18:12,399
Pull over now.

1184
01:18:16,501 --> 01:18:18,029
Hold on, all right?

1185
01:18:44,131 --> 01:18:45,131
Get out.

1186
01:18:45,174 --> 01:18:46,174
Get out.

1187
