This is not a good idea.

1188
01:19:12,703 --> 01:19:13,703
Crap!

1189
01:19:19,932 --> 01:19:21,983
Get out of the vehicle now!

1190
01:19:22,087 --> 01:19:23,860
Get out.

1191
01:19:23,965 --> 01:19:24,972
Now.

1192
01:19:25,075 --> 01:19:26,034
Get over there.

1193
01:19:26,049 --> 01:19:27,049
Get over there.

1194
01:19:27,126 --> 01:19:28,969
Stand right there, right here.

1195
01:19:29,073 --> 01:19:30,637
Move the car to the driveway, sweetheart.

1196
01:19:30,742 --> 01:19:32,374
It's blocking me.

1197
01:19:32,479 --> 01:19:33,905
I love you.

1198
01:19:34,008 --> 01:19:35,001
I love you too.

1199
01:19:35,016 --> 01:19:36,016
Come on.

1200
01:19:39,605 --> 01:19:41,551
Woo hoo, it's been a while.

1201
01:19:54,481 --> 01:19:56,288
Where's the site team?

1202
01:19:56,392 --> 01:19:57,888
30 miles away from the plant.

1203
01:19:57,992 --> 01:19:59,520
Great, close enough to be killed,

1204
01:19:59,625 --> 01:20:00,806
too far to be of any use.

1205
01:20:03,656 --> 01:20:04,656
I'm sorry.

1206
01:20:29,445 --> 01:20:31,497
We just lost another hose, Corrine.

1207
01:20:31,601 --> 01:20:33,582
Three men have passed out from the heat.

1208
01:20:33,686 --> 01:20:34,765
We're down to minutes here.

1209
01:20:38,379 --> 01:20:39,908
I got you.

1210
01:20:40,012 --> 01:20:41,333
Here we go.

1211
01:20:41,437 --> 01:20:44,078
Let's get him out of here.

1212
01:20:44,183 --> 01:20:45,295
It's too hot!

1213
01:20:45,400 --> 01:20:50,126
I don't know how long I can hold this.

1214
01:20:50,231 --> 01:20:51,189
Take five, Jesse.

1215
01:20:51,204 --> 01:20:52,351
That's an order.

1216
01:20:52,455 --> 01:20:53,846
We're going to need more
men to man those hoses.

1217
01:20:53,950 --> 01:20:55,409
We'll try.

1218
01:20:55,513 --> 01:20:57,286
They're going to need containment suits.

1219
01:20:57,390 --> 01:20:59,998
OK.

1220
01:21:23,249 --> 01:21:26,865
Jake, follow me.

1221
01:21:26,969 --> 01:21:27,969
Down there.

1222
01:21:44,590 --> 01:21:45,584
It's a water hose.

1223
01:21:45,599 --> 01:21:46,522
Yeah.

1224
01:21:46,537 --> 01:21:47,684
Improvising.

1225
01:21:47,789 --> 01:21:49,422
We just lost another one, Corrine.

1226
01:21:49,526 --> 01:21:50,777
We're not going to make it.

1227
01:21:50,882 --> 01:21:53,314
I don't have time for that right now, Gail.

1228
01:21:53,418 --> 01:21:54,984
Corrine, is this under control?

1229
01:21:55,087 --> 01:21:56,130
- Yeah.
- I'll go with them.

1230
01:21:56,234 --> 01:21:57,234
All right.

1231
01:22:01,169 --> 01:22:02,127
I got it.

1232
