1235
01:22:16,080 --> 01:22:17,610
Keep holding on.

1236
01:22:22,754 --> 01:22:25,396
Keep it in the pool.

1237
01:22:25,500 --> 01:22:26,500
Hang on.

1238
01:22:31,130 --> 01:22:32,172
It's too hot!

1239
01:22:36,726 --> 01:22:39,019
Jake, I've heard this room is radioactive,
