1240
01:22:39,123 --> 01:22:40,123
Yeah.

1241
01:23:00,187 --> 01:23:01,299
It's not filling!

1242
01:23:04,915 --> 01:23:06,478
Keep it going.

1243
01:23:13,046 --> 01:23:14,681
Warning... fuel rods

1244
01:23:14,786 --> 01:23:17,322
