1249
01:23:59,030 --> 01:24:00,525
We're losing it.

1250
01:24:00,629 --> 01:24:01,776
We're losing it.

1251
01:24:05,843 --> 01:24:07,964
Start, you son of a bitch!

1252
01:24:33,475 --> 01:24:34,475
We got it!

1253
01:24:34,518 --> 01:24:35,873
We got it! We got it!

1254
01:24:35,977 --> 01:24:36,977
We got it!

1255
01:24:37,019 --> 01:24:38,019
We got it!

1256
01:24:38,062 --> 01:24:39,175
We got it!

1257
01:24:44,318 --> 01:24:46,891
That's all we were waiting for, right?

1258
01:24:46,995 --> 01:24:48,385
I think so.

1259
01:24:48,489 --> 01:24:50,436
Can you help my men over there?

1260
01:24:50,541 --> 01:24:53,565
Yeah.

1261
01:24:53,669 --> 01:24:54,669
Oh my god.

1262
01:24:54,712 --> 01:24:56,275
God, I hate this job.

1263
01:25:03,644 --> 01:25:06,077
We did it.

1264
01:25:06,181 --> 01:25:07,815
We did it!

1265
01:25:07,919 --> 01:25:08,919
We did it!

1266
01:25:22,482 --> 01:25:23,482
Hey.

1267
01:25:27,069 --> 01:25:28,112
Hey.

1268
01:25:55,919 --> 01:25:58,212
Nice work.

1269
01:25:58,316 --> 01:25:59,316
Yeah.

1270
01:26:02,383 --> 01:26:03,383
You too.

1271
01:26:13,435 --> 01:26:15,452
Helman-Klein just reported in.

1272
01:26:15,556 --> 01:26:17,572
They're damaged, but they're stable.

1273
01:26:17,676 --> 01:26:22,159
They're downgrading back to stage one.

1274
01:26:22,263 --> 01:26:23,342
